name: Suaré All Over 3M Tee
description:
Hand crafted from the finest 3M material on the market, we've managed to make possibly the most electrifying tee to date. This Unisex tee features an "invisible zipper" running up along the side, as well as another invisible zipper along the neck area, for the most perfect and comfortable fit possible. As seen in our other products, our "All Over 3M Tee" will feature our classic black patch brand name stitched along the back neck area, keeping the front as sleek and clean as possible. 

Please Note: These shirts are created with a longer length then a normal shirt, but still maintain the same width as a normal shirt. 

This is a custom hand crafted piece. All pieces are made one by one, by hand. Therefore; all pieces take 1-2 weeks to complete. Thank You.

CARE INSTRUCTIONS:
-IRON ON LOW HEAT INSIDE OUT
-HAND WASH
-AIR DRY ONLY
-DO NOT DRYCLEAN

***Make sure to ALWAYS unzip-per both the neck and side area of the shirt before putting the shirt on***

*Failure to follow these care instructions will result in damage to the shirt.

name: Suaré 3M Simplistic Tee
description:
This is the introduction shirt to the SuaréNewYork S/S Collection. Releasing in limited quantities, these 100% cotton - individually made tops have been created to be worn in any aspect of fashion. The branded name stitched in the back keeps the front sleek and clean, while still representing where this shirt originated from. The sleeves stay striped with high quality 3m reflective material, making sure your outfit separates from the rest, in the purest of day & the darkness of night


Care Instructions: 
-NOT MACHINE WASHABLE
-DRY CLEAN ONLY
-WHEN IRONING, IRON INSIDE OUT ON LOW HEAT.

*Failure to follow these care instructions, will result in damage to the shirt.

name: Suaré 3M Box Logo Tee
description:
As the second piece in the SuaréNewYork S/S Collection, the Suaré 3M Box Logo Tee mixes high end inspired fashion & simplicity, with pure elegance. Not only is this shirts appearance extremely sleek and clean, but it is also bringing back the 3M feature from the first shirt release, and using it in a whole different way. This design will be placed on a White 6 oz. 100% Cotton Tee, with double-needle bottom hem and sleeves stitching. Giving you the most comfortable wear of shirt as possible. Shirt is made to be worn unisex. Im sure many people have noticed how quick the last piece has sold out; you aren't going to want to miss this one. 



CARE INSTRUCTIONS: 
-DRY CLEAN FOR BEST RESULTS

OR

-MACHINE WASH INSIDE OUT, WITH WHITES
-DO NOT BLEACH
-LINE DRY
-WHEN IRONING, IRON INSIDE OUT ON LOW HEAT.

*Failure to follow these care instructions, will result in damage to the shirt.
